EvolutionaryScale Cambrian Open License Agreement

The ESM C (ESMC) 300M model weights loaded and served by this wrapper are
licensed by EvolutionaryScale, PBC ("ES") under the EvolutionaryScale Cambrian
Open License Agreement. The full, controlling agreement is published at:

    https://www.evolutionaryscale.ai/policies/cambrian-open-license-agreement

The weights are NOT MIT-licensed. (The separate `esm` Python package source
code is MIT-licensed, but that does not extend to the model weights.) Review the
full agreement before any commercial or production use.

Required notice
---------------
    The ESMC 300M Model is licensed under the EvolutionaryScale Cambrian Open
    License Agreement.

"Built with ESM" attribution
----------------------------
You must prominently display "Built with ESM" on any application programming
interface, model, workflow, website, user interface, blog post, about page,
product documentation, or other media or interface that incorporates the
Licensed Model IP.

Naming of derivative works
--------------------------
You must include "ESM" at the beginning of the title of any Derivative Works
(without reusing the licensor's specific name together with a version number,
model-size indication, letter, or similar designation).

Notices to retain
-----------------
You must retain, in the Source form of any Derivative Works you distribute, all
copyright, patent, trademark, and attribution notices from the Source form of
the Licensed Model.

Licensor: EvolutionaryScale, PBC.

