NOTE TO MAINTAINERS: This file summarizes the key obligations of the
EvolutionaryScale Cambrian Open License Agreement (the "Built with ESM"
attribution, the "ESM"-prefixed naming requirement, and the required notice
line) reconstructed from the published agreement and the ESM C 300M model card.
It is NOT the full legal text. Before this repository goes public, confirm the
exact, current clause wording against the upstream Cambrian Open License
Agreement and consider vendoring the complete agreement text here.
